<p class="govuk-body">Thank you for contacting HM Courts and Tribunals Service (HMCTS) Jury Central Summoning Bureau.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">As discussed today, we can confirm that we've made a referral to our partner organisation, We Are Group, to provide you with support for the online appeal form. They do not provide legal advice.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">You will receive a call back from We Are Group within the next 2 working days. If you wish to contact them yourself, this can be done by:</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>Telephone: 03300 160051</li>
  <li>We Are Group's opening hours. Monday - Friday 09.00 - 17.00</li>
  <li>Email: support@wearegroup.com</li>
  <li>Or text "FORM" to 60777</li>
  <li>Website: <a class="govuk-link" href="https://www.wearegroup.com/digital_support">https://www.wearegroup.com/digital_support</a></li>
</ul>

<p class="govuk-body">Please do not reply to this message as this number is not monitored.</p>
